Class DataModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.sfgmbh.datalayer.core.model.DataModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IntfAppObservable

    public class DataModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements IntfAppObservable
    The main class to manage the data handler in which interested objects that implement the IntfAppOberserver interfaces may register and get updated on any relevant changes from the corresponding data handler.
